These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, black
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, pop
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the owner of the frog is the fan of pop##1
5. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Color   | black   | blood-red  |
| Music-Genre   | pop | soul |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Flower     | azalea    | balloon-flower   |

