.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different games are played: go, whist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Game         | whist        | go  |
| Movie-Genre           | animation | thriller  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Cigar   | vegafina     | ritmeester   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

